<h3>Single-Stream Recycling</h3>
<p>Single-Stream Recycling is easy!</p>
<p>You can put all your recycling together loose in your large recycle toter. We are always looking to recycle more items, so check our <a href="#" class="web-link">Recyclopedia</a> to help find what can be recycled and reused.</p>
<h3>Garbage Bin</h3>
<p>Each household has been assigned one free garbage toter. You may buy additional garbage toters for <strong>$70 each</strong>. To purchase additional toters, please call <span class="phone-link">203-977-4620</span>.</p>
